<title>Bootstrap Navbar Plugin - Examples</title>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container mt-4 mb-5">
  <h1>Bootstrap Navbar Plugin - Esempi</h1>
  <p class="lead">Tutti i casi d'uso del plugin <code>bootstrapNavbar</code> con pagine demo interattive.</p>

  <hr>

  <%# ========== NAVBAR TYPES ========== %>
  <h2 class="mt-4">Tipi di Navbar</h2>

  <div class="row g-4 mt-1">

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-layout-navbar"></i> Horizontal Light</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Navbar orizzontale con tema chiaro, <code>bg-body-tertiary</code>, <code>expandAt: md</code>, container centrato.</p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled small text-muted">
            <li>Dropdown con divider</li>
            <li>Separator tra items</li>
            <li>Container non-fluid</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a href="/navbarExamples/horizontal.ejs" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Apri demo</a>
          <span class="badge bg-light text-dark ms-1">type: horizontal</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-layout-sidebar"></i> Vertical Sidebar</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Sidebar verticale dark con layout flex. Sezioni top/bottom separate da <code>&lt;hr&gt;</code>.</p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled small text-muted">
            <li>Dropdown in verticale</li>
            <li>Auth: items condizionali</li>
            <li>sections.left = top, .right = bottom</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a href="/navbarExamples/vertical.ejs" class="btn btn-dark btn-sm">Apri demo</a>
          <span class="badge bg-light text-dark ms-1">type: vertical</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-layout-sidebar-inset"></i> Offcanvas Responsive</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Offcanvas che sopra <code>lg</code> diventa navbar inline. Sotto <code>lg</code> pannello scorrevole.</p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled small text-muted">
            <li>offcanvasAlways: false</li>
            <li>bg-success (verde)</li>
            <li>Auth: Cart e Account condizionali</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a href="/navbarExamples/offcanvas.ejs" class="btn btn-success btn-sm">Apri demo</a>
          <span class="badge bg-light text-dark ms-1">type: offcanvas</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-list"></i> Offcanvas Always</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Hamburger SEMPRE visibile (non diventa mai inline). Offcanvas da destra (<code>end</code>).</p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled small text-muted">
            <li>offcanvasAlways: true</li>
            <li>position: end (da destra)</li>
            <li>Confronto tabellare true vs false</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a href="/navbarExamples/offcanvasAlways.ejs" class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm">Apri demo</a>
          <span class="badge bg-light text-dark ms-1">type: offcanvas</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ========== FEATURES ========== %>
  <h2 class="mt-5">Features</h2>

  <div class="row g-4 mt-1">

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-danger">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock"></i> Auth/Roles Filtering</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Dimostra tutte le opzioni di visibilit&agrave;: <code>showWhen</code>, <code>requiresAuth</code>, <code>allowedRoles</code>.</p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled small text-muted">
            <li>Tabella stato sessione in tempo reale</li>
            <li>Dropdown con sub-items filtrati per ruolo</li>
            <li>Root, Admin, Editor, Custom roles</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a href="/navbarExamples/authHeavy.ejs" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm">Apri demo</a>
          <span class="badge bg-light text-dark ms-1">auth + roles</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
      <div class="card h-100 border-warning">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title"><i class="bi bi-sliders"></i> Settings Overrides</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Stesso file JSON5, 5 render diversi con <code>settingsOverrides</code>. Cambia type, bg, expandAt, autoActive al volo.</p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled small text-muted">
            <li>5 varianti dello stesso menu</li>
            <li>Override: bgClass, colorScheme, type</li>
            <li>Override: expandAt, autoActive, id</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer">
          <a href="/navbarExamples/settingsOverrides.ejs" class="btn btn-warning btn-sm">Apri demo</a>
          <span class="badge bg-light text-dark ms-1">settingsOverrides</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ========== QUICK REFERENCE ========== %>
  <h2 class="mt-5">Quick Reference</h2>

  <div class="card mt-3">
    <div class="card-header">Sintassi EJS</div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <pre class="mb-0"><code><%# Render base %>
&lt;%- passData.plugin.bootstrapNavbar.render({name: 'main'}, passData) %&gt;

<%# Con settingsOverrides %>
&lt;%- passData.plugin.bootstrapNavbar.render({
  name: 'main',
  settingsOverrides: { type: 'offcanvas', bgClass: 'bg-dark' }
}, passData) %&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card mt-3">
    <div class="card-header">Struttura navbar.{name}.json5</div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <pre class="mb-0"><code>{
  "settings": {
    "type": "horizontal",          // horizontal | vertical | offcanvas
    "colorScheme": "dark",         // dark | light
    "bgClass": "bg-primary",      // qualsiasi classe Bootstrap bg-*
    "expandAt": "lg",              // sm | md | lg | xl | xxl
    "containerClass": "container-fluid",
    "autoActive": true,
    "offcanvasAlways": false,      // solo per type: offcanvas
    "position": "start",           // start | end
    "id": "navbarMain"
  },
  "sections": {
    "left": [ /* items */ ],
    "right": [ /* items */ ]
  }
}</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card mt-3">
    <div class="card-header">Tipi di Items</div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <pre class="mb-0"><code>// Link semplice
{ "label": "Home", "href": "/", "icon": "&lt;i class='bi bi-house'&gt;&lt;/i&gt;" }

// Link con target
{ "label": "Docs", "href": "https://example.com", "target": "_blank" }

// Dropdown
{ "type": "dropdown", "label": "Menu", "items": [ /* sub-items */ ] }

// Divider (dentro dropdown)
{ "type": "divider" }

// Separator (tra items nella barra)
{ "type": "separator" }

// Visibilit&agrave; condizionale
{ "label": "Login", "href": "/login", "showWhen": "unauthenticated" }
{ "label": "Profile", "href": "/profile", "showWhen": "authenticated" }
{ "label": "Admin", "href": "/admin", "requiresAuth": true, "allowedRoles": [0, 1] }</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

